{% cell xaoxuu, https://xaoxuu.com, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xaoxuu/cdn-assets/avatar/avatar.png %}
{% endbtns %}
```
2.或者含有图标的按钮
```markdown
{% btns rounded grid5 %}
{% cell 下载源码, /, fas fa-download %}
{% cell 查看文档, /, fas fa-book-open %}
{% endbtns %}
```

